  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cleaner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform general cleaning tasks including vacuuming, mopping, sweeping floors, and dusting all surfaces, furniture, and fixtures.</p></li><li><p>Empty all trash and recycling bins and ensure proper disposal of waste.</p></li><li><p>Monitor cleaning supply levels and inform the supervisor when replenishment is needed.</p></li><li><p>Identify and report any maintenance issues or safety hazards (e.g., leaks, damages) encountered during cleaning rounds.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p><ul><li><p>No prior experience required; on-the-job training will be provided.</p></li><li><p>Ability to handle basic cleaning equipment and materials.</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and a commitment to maintaining high hygiene standards.</p></li><li><p>Reliability, honesty, and the ability to work independently with minimal supervision.</p></li><li><p>Good physical condition, capable of standing, bending, and lifting for extended periods.</p></li><li><p>No work pass quota.</p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
